snippet.title: CONNECT : 30.01.24 Trailer
snippet.description: CONNECT is an RPG inspired by Eathbound( Mother 2 ) : A story about unexpected phenomena that occur in the world. Billy, the person affected by this matter, must set out to find the truth of the phenomenon. So he found out that....what had happened was so surreal.
